    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div id="section-faq" class="section-faq section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-10 offset-md-1">
            <div class="section-header mb-30">
              <h5>Frequently Asked Questions</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="panel-group" id="exampleAccordionDefault" aria-multiselectable="true" role="tablist">
              <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-heading" id="exampleHeadingDefaultOne" role="tab">
                  <a class="panel-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#exampleCollapseDefaultOne" data-parent="#exampleAccordionDefault"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleCollapseDefaultOne">
                    WHY DON'T YOU HAVE ICO LIKE OTHER START-UP PROJECTS?
                  </a>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="exampleCollapseDefaultOne" aria-labelledby="exampleHeadingDefaultOne"
                  role="tabpanel">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    We don't conduct ICO as of the moment since we are still working with the regulations in our
                    jurisdiction, however, we are already on the process of getting the license from respective
                    agencies. Conducting ICO without license would only hurt us getting the license.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-heading" id="exampleHeadingDefaultTwo" role="tab">
                  <a class="panel-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#exampleCollapseDefaultTwo" data-parent="#exampleAccordionDefault"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleCollapseDefaultTwo">
                    WHY DO YOU HAVE FOUR PLATFORMS?
                  </a>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="exampleCollapseDefaultTwo" aria-labelledby="exampleHeadingDefaultTwo"
                  role="tabpanel">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    We made the SparkX and SparkRoom platforms to reach the vast majority of the unbanked population.
                    According to World Bank findings, financial illiteracy is one of the factors that hinders many to
                    be financially included. With SparkX that will serve as their digital wallet, SparkRoom will
                    provide courses and programs to promote financial literacy.
                    SparkPlace aims to introduce a new way of shopping using the blockchain technology and reducing the
                    cost of doing online marketplace like listing fees and shopping fees. SparkPlay aims to give
                    players and consumers the power to have a reward that will return the value of their in-app
                    purchases unlike existing paid games and application from different application store.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-heading" id="exampleHeadingDefaultThree" role="tab">
                  <a class="panel-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#exampleCollapseDefaultThree"
                    data-parent="#exampleAccordionDefault" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleCollapseDefaultThree">
                    WHAT MAKES SPARKX DIFFERENT FROM OTHER PAYMENT GATEWAYS?
                  </a>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="exampleCollapseDefaultThree" aria-labelledby="exampleHeadingDefaultThree"
                  role="tabpanel">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    SparkX unlike any other payment gateways not only allows peer-to-peer transfer and remittance, and
                    paying utility bills, SparkX will also be integrated to our other platforms and can be used for
                    micropayments to our partner brick-and-mortar and brick-and-click stores and soon, to pay for
                    government dues and fees.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-heading" id="exampleHeadingDefaultFour" role="tab">
                  <a class="panel-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#exampleCollapseDefaultFour"
                    data-parent="#exampleAccordionDefault" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleCollapseDefaultFour">
                    IS SPRK A SECURITY TOKEN OR A UTILITY TOKEN?
                  </a>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="exampleCollapseDefaultFour" aria-labelledby="exampleHeadingDefaultFour"
                  role="tabpanel">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    SparkPoint Token or SPRK is a utility token. It has its own function not just in the application
                    but also in the real world through our partners. SPRK can be use to pay products and services.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-heading" id="exampleHeadingDefaultOne" role="tab">
                  <a class="panel-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#accordion-faq-2One" data-parent="#accordion-faq-2"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-faq-2One">
                    WHAT IS SPRK TOKEN AND HOW CAN I USE IT?
                  </a>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="accordion-faq-2One" aria-labelledby="exampleHeadingDefaultOne"
                  role="tabpanel">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    SPRK token is SparkPoint Ecosystem's utility coin to be used in different transactions in and out
                    our platforms. SPRK token can be use for transaction fees in SparkX, enrolment in SparkRoom,
                    purchasing products or services in SparkPlace and purchasing games and in-game purchases in
                    SparkPlay. Aside from these main function, SPRK will also be accepted as payment for our partner
                    stores and service providers.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="panel-group" id="accordion-faq-2" aria-multiselectable="true" role="tablist">
              <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-heading" id="exampleHeadingDefaultTwo" role="tab">
                  <a class="panel-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#accordion-faq-2Two" data-parent="#accordion-faq-2"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-faq-2Two">
                    DO I NEED DIFFERENT WALLET TO ACCESS ALL PLATFORMS?
                  </a>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="accordion-faq-2Two" aria-labelledby="exampleHeadingDefaultTwo"
                  role="tabpanel">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    No. SparkPoint Ecosystem will have its own digital and e-wallet called SparkX that is integrated to
                    all other platforms in the application.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-heading" id="exampleHeadingDefaultThree" role="tab">
                  <a class="panel-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#accordion-faq-2Three" data-parent="#accordion-faq-2"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-faq-2Three">
                    WHERE CAN I DOWNLOAD THE SPARKPOINT ECOSYSTEM MOBILE APPLICATION?
                  </a>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="accordion-faq-2Three" aria-labelledby="exampleHeadingDefaultThree"
                  role="tabpanel">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    Our application is still in development and and will soon be available in Google Play and Apple App
                    Store.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-heading" id="exampleHeadingDefaultFour" role="tab">
                  <a class="panel-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#accordion-faq-2Four" data-parent="#accordion-faq-2"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-faq-2Four">
                    HOW CAN I CONTACT YOU IF I NEED HELP?
                  </a>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="accordion-faq-2Four" aria-labelledby="exampleHeadingDefaultFour"
                  role="tabpanel">
                  <div class="panel-body">
                    You may reach us trough Telegram t.me/SparkPointOfficial or send an e-mail at support@sparkpoint.io
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-heading" id="exampleHeadingDefaultFour" role="tab">
                  <a class="panel-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#accordion-faq-2Six" data-parent="#accordion-faq-2"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-faq-2Four">
                    I HAVE A SUGGESTION, WHERE CAN I SEND IT?
                  </a>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="accordion-faq-2Six" aria-labelledby="exampleHeadingDefaultFour"
